snippet.textDisplay: @DEON MINOTT BTS stands for Bangtan Sonyeondan in Korean which translates to bulletproof boy scouts in english. Bangtan means resistant to bullets so it means to block out stereotypes, criticisms, and expectations that are aimed at young people like bullets, to preserve the value and ideals of today's young people.  In 2017 they also added the meaning of BTS as Beyond the Scene, but I think most people prefer the original meaning of BTS as it has more meaning for the fans. They have had 3 movies that have the BTS acronym Burn the Stage, Bring the Soul, and Break the Silence but those aren't the meaning of BTS the group name itself.  Hope that helped, feel free to ask any other questions you may have.
